OL,3,CUK-wide E.coli outbreak: What do we
OL,4,Cknow so far?
OL,6,FA statement from the UKHSA added:
OL,7,F"Based on the wide geographic spread
OL,8,Fof cases, it is most likely that this
OL,9,Foutbreak is linked to a nationally
OL,10,Fdistributed food item or multiple food
OL,11,Fitems."
OL,13,FIt can also be spread by touching
OL,14,Finfected animals or coming into
OL,15,Fcontact with their faeces.
OL,17,FComing into contact with infected
OL,18,Fpeople, drinking water from
OL,19,Finadequately treated water supplies,
OL,20,Fand swimming in contaminated water can
OL,21,Falso spread E.coli.
