OL,3,CUK-wide E.coli outbreak: What do we
OL,4,Cknow so far?
OL,6,FThe UKHSA, however, has said there was
OL,7,Fcurrently no evidence linking the
OL,8,Foutbreak to open farms, drinking water
OL,9,For swimming in contaminated sea, lakes
OL,10,For rivers.
OL,12,FHow dangerous is E.Coli?
OL,14,FSome strains produce toxins that can
OL,15,Fmake people very ill, such as Stec.
OL,16,FPeople infected with Stec can suffer
OL,17,Fdiarrhoea, and about 50% of cases have
OL,18,Fbloody diarrhoea.
