OL,3,CUK-wide E.coli outbreak: What do we
OL,4,Cknow so far?
OL,6,FSome people can become infected but
OL,7,Fdon't develop any symptoms.
OL,9,FWhat are medical professionals and the
OL,10,Fgovernment saying?
OL,12,FTrish Mannes, incident director at
OL,13,FUKHSA, said: "If you have diarrhoea
OL,14,Fand vomiting, you can take steps to
OL,15,Favoid passing it on to family and
OL,16,Ffriends.
OL,18,F"NHS.uk has information on what to do
OL,19,Fif you have symptoms and when to seek
OL,20,Fmedical advice.
