OL,3,CUK-wide E.coli outbreak: What do we
OL,4,Cknow so far?
OL,6,F"Do not return to work, school or
OL,7,Fnursery until 48 hours after your
OL,8,Fsymptoms have stopped."
OL,10,FJim McMenamin, Head of Health
OL,11,FProtection (infection Services),
OL,12,FPublic Health Scotland, said: "To help
OL,13,Fstop infections like E. coli from
OL,14,Fspreading, we advise regular hand
OL,15,Fwashing using soap and water,
OL,16,Fparticularly after using the toilet
OL,17,Fand before preparing food.
